Text:
are saleem bhai help yaar...

baat kuch aisi hai ki maine aap ki movie 63% download karli hai....aur mai aise hi by chance uska folder try kia open karne ko ki dekhu quality kaisi hai par nahi uha...likha aara hai "path dont exist "..

phir maine utorrent ke through open karne ki koshih ki by "right click kark ke open containing folder" yeh likha aaya ki file open nahi ho sakti file exist hi nahi karti...par download ho rahi hai speed bhi aa rahi hai..folder bhi hai but none of them is opening 

ab batao mein kya karoo agar aap kuch help kar sakte ho toh ..please...

aapko pata hai itna bada size hai ki vapis download karna bahut mushkil hai..kyonki meri internet download speed max..50 kb/s ...please bhai koi upaye de do...kya mein download continue rakhoo ..yeah sab kuch bekar ho gaya ....2 din aur 2 ghante laga 63% aane par...please reply karo very urgent..

@one121 bro agar aisi problem show kar rha hai to tum sirf torrent ko remove karo utorrent se (without deleting files) and fir se torrent ko download ke liye lagao usi directory par lagao... fir check karo... :)
aur agar ye discription samajh nahi aai to facebook par group me aakar discuss karo we will sort out your problem

@meguil

bhai jo aapne kaha hai woh maine try kiya par kuch farq nahi para utorrent ne download check kiya jab maine naya torrent dala (jaise aapne bataya )par abhi bhi wahi kahani hai speed aa rahi hai par files open nahi ho rahi (i guess corrupted ho gay hai)...abh nahi lagta koi aur rasta hai 

isliye ab main doobara hi download kar raha hoo kyonki bahut achi series hai aur quality bhi acchi hogi kyonki aap  ne joh upload ki hai... 

par bhai ek problem hai ki aap ki seeding ab tak 91 % ke kareeb ho gayi hai....par jab 100% ho jaye please seeding rokna mat..kyonki mujhe lagta hai aur shayed aap bhi iss baat se sahmat hoge ki bahut kum guyz seeding karte hai (zaada tar hit and run karte hai)  

so please aap seeding mat rokna complete karne ke baad kyonki bahut bada size hai isliye..

SORRY BHAI...mein faceook nahi use karta par mujko pata hai ki aap log FACEBOOK pe ho....but sorry again mein use nahi karta..

and thanks for your reply..aap ne time nikal kar reply kiya uske liye bahut zayada sukhriya..

thank you and i guess this time movie will work for me
okay bro hum seeding tab tak nhi rokenge jab tak 70 ke karib seeder nhi ho jatey.. :)
thank you bro...i will try too complete as fast as i can

@one121 bro seeding 100% complte ho gai hai bt main abi tak is ko seeding kar raha hon aur jab tak 50GB seed nai ho jata abi 30GB seed hua hai aur han bro jab movie complte ho jay to ap reply kar dena bhai kafi baar is tarhan se ho jata hai k movie jab tak complte na ho tab tak wo open nai hoti hai
agr ap ne result aur audio check karna hai to main is me alg se sample ka link diya tha download kar k check kar sakte ho :)

@s4saleem

bhai bura mat manna par seeding complete karke hi toh apne galti ki...complete hone se pehle speed aa rahi thi puri (50kb/s) ab kabhi 25 kabhi 3o , 40 kabhi 15  aise aa rahi hai(meri maximum download speed 50 kb/s hai)...sorry par yeh baat sach hai joh maine likhi hai upar....par mujhe pata hai aap logo ke upar bahut pressure hota hai  (jald se jald complete karke friends tak movie pahuchane ka), aur isme aap ki kohi bhi galti nahi hai....again sorry but just as a friend i have written that 

bhai joh aap ko laga wahi mujko bhi lag raha tha ki ek baar complete karke dekho ...shayed phir open ho jaye...par bhai woh path hi exist nahi dikhara tha ...jaise maine woh (d drive)mein save kari thi aapki (lord) par woh folder bhi open nahi karne de rahi thi 

...isliye mein 4 gb aur download karke risk nahi lena chahat tha aur maine apne  bhai se bhi poocha tha (usne bhi dekhne ke baad kaha nahi ho sakti aur mere pe hasne lag gaya )  maine  7.50 gb ke kareeb download kar liya tha aur 4.50 ke kareeb rehgaya tha...phir main aur kya karta maine socha aage open nayi hui to ...isse accha hai doobara hi shuru karo...shayed tab kismat mein hi nahi thi aur kya

ab maine doobara shuru kar toh diya hai..par yeh nahi keh sakta kab tak complete hoga....48 % ho chuka hai(1 din 17hr).. ab 5 hi seeder hai aur speed na poochoh toh accha hai...(lol)..koshish toh hai jald se jald complete karne ki par dekho kab tak hoti hai...

bhai jab bhi hogi aap ko zarror bata dooga...aur bhai request hai kabhi kabhi beach mein 1 ya 2 ghanto ke liye seed kar dena ...saayed thodi der ke liye speed mein farq par jaye

thank you aap ne comment kiya ...and dekho kab tak hota  ..thanks again

aur bhai last time jab maine download kar raha tha toh apne (pc) pe  sayed is wajjah se woh itni badi file ko contain nahi kar paa rah tha...iss bar mein apne lappy(64 bit home) mein kar raha hu aur beach mein (open contaning folder) se file bhi check kar raha hoo ...aur ab tak sabh kuch sahi hi chal raha hai ...file open ho rahi hai...finger crossed

aur bhai aapko sample dalne ki zarrorat nahi hai maine quality dekh liye hai bahut acchi hai...thanks for that too
ab 17 seeders dikha raha...lolol....mujhe lagta hai ki ab main complete karluga..thnks..

@one121 bhai main to 16 din se ab tak seeding kar raha hon han bhai ye hai k jab full seed ho jati hai to peers ziyada hone ki waja se speed nai milti hai bro 8 logo ne 100% hone k baad seed per laga rakhi hai per kisi ko b un ki seed speed nai ja rahi hai bro main 150KB ps se seed kar raha hon aur karta rahon ga jab tak ye movie 60 se 70GB seed nai ho jati hai main yaar akela hi is ko seed kar raha hon is liye downloader ziyada hain sab k pas 150KB taqseem ho jati hai ap d/l per lagy rakho main seeding per lagai hui hai aur han main is ko kal apne kisi aik ya 2 aur dosto ko seeding k liye deta hon han kuch time me li8 problem ki waja se seed nai ho pati hai pakistani time note kar lo is time me seeding nai ho gi 
05:00AM
07:00AM
12:00PM
02:00PM
06:00PM
09:00PM
is time k elawa har waqt seeding jari o sari rahy gi :)

@s4saleem

4 days and 41 minutes lage complete karne mein ab jaake ho gayi hai....

thanks to you (saleem bhai) and meguil bro...really thanks quality bahut acchi hai thanks you
